init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You don't know if it's real or a prank.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But you can't help but feel a sense of duty.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The phone rings and a voice answers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm afraid I'm going to need your help."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I know this is hard to believe, but I'm not dead.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm alive and well, but I'm in a bit of a bind.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Well, I'm in a bit of a situation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm not sure how I got here, but I'm not alone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Well, there's a bunch of other people here.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm not sure who they are, but I think they are all famous.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: JFK pleads with you to reconsider.
